OL,3,C'My life's on hold': Man yet to move
OL,4,Cback in three years after fire damaged
OL,5,Cflat
OL,7,FA man from Basingstoke says his life
OL,8,Fis "on hold", as he's yet to move back
OL,9,Finto his property, three years after
OL,10,Fit was severely damaged by a fire.
OL,12,FNigel Lunn's property was one of many
OL,13,Fimpacted by the fire which affected a
OL,14,Fblock of flats on Oakridge Road in May
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FMr Lunn has been living in temporary
OL,18,Faccommodation arranged by VIVID, who
OL,19,Fown the building, ever since, but says
OL,20,Fthat his flat is still not ready to
OL,21,Fmove back to.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
