FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781590674
OL,3,C'My life's on hold': Man yet to move
OL,4,Cback in three years after fire damaged
OL,5,Cflat
OL,7,FIn addition, the lease on his
OL,8,Ftemporary accommodation is due to end
OL,9,Fin July, and Mr Lunn is yet to hear if
OL,10,Fit will be extended.
OL,12,FMr Lunn said: "I don't really know
OL,13,Fwhat's going on, because they keep
OL,14,Fchanging the tenancy end date for my
OL,15,Faccommodation."
OL,17,F"I've tried to get hold of VIVID to
OL,18,Ffind out what's going on, but I
OL,19,Fhaven't spoken with them since January.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781590674
OL,3,C'My life's on hold': Man yet to move
OL,4,Cback in three years after fire damaged
OL,5,Cflat
OL,7,F"I don't know where I'm going after
OL,8,FJuly."
OL,10,FMr Lunn continued: "My life's on hold,
OL,11,FI can't plan anything.
OL,13,F"As I've said before I've been wanting
OL,14,Fto retire for the last three years,
OL,15,Fand I can't do it, because one of the
OL,16,Fthings that I need to do for
OL,17,Fretirement is to sell the flat."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
