SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781590674
OL,3,C'My life's on hold': Man yet to move
OL,4,Cback in three years after fire damaged
OL,5,Cflat
OL,7,FIn a statement Alex Nagle, Customer
OL,8,FService Director at VIVID, said:
OL,9,F"We've continued to stay in close
OL,10,Fcontact with our customers throughout,
OL,11,Fkeeping them updated as things have
OL,12,Fchanged, especially where delays have
OL,13,Fbeen outside of our control.
OL,15,F"There have been some setbacks with
OL,16,Fgas and electric connections.
OL,18,F"We'll continue to share updates as
OL,19,Fthings progress and look forward to
OL,20,Fwelcoming our customers back to their
OL,21,Fhomes."
